<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <title>Evernight</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      padding-top: 40px;
    }

    .image-container {
      width: 80%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: -5px 5px 20px rgba(210, 210, 210, 0.8);
    }

    .image-container img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .card {
      width: 400px;
      box-shadow: -10px 10px 25px rgba(210, 210, 210, .9);
      border-radius: 35px;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 50px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .card h2 {
      color: #20b2aa;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .card button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: #20b2aa;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1em;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    .card button:hover {
      background: #1a9a9a;
    }

    .card a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 10px 30px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: #20b2aa;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="image-container">
    <img src="/images/evernight.jpg" alt="Admin Banner">
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>「亲爱的三月七」</h2>
    
    <p>亲爱的三月七，</p>
    
    <p>抵达翁法罗斯，并非一场意外。<br>
    我们要做的事，也与过往无异。</p>
    
    <p>往前看，是杳无人烟的败城，哭天抢地的生灵，看不见未来的眼睛。<br>
    向后望，是融化记忆的罅隙，窥觎非望的窃贼，无法逃离的过去。</p>
    
    <p>「我该如何向前走，继续开拓未来…」</p>
    
    <p>很简单，就像我为你做的那样<br>
    ——让「忘却」令「记忆」安息。</p>
    
    <p>晚安。</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>